<br>
I'm reminded of an incident long ago on FV.  Bjond was walking out of Najena and noticed a VERY snazzily dressed Inky fighting his way in down to BC with a few more obviously newbie types nearby.  Naturally, I assumed he was a high level slumming or helping PL or something (I didn't even target or /con him).  I just waved and ran out.  Turned out he had recently rerolled and was slain by the ogre guard and skeleton there.<br>
<br>
Ooops.  Oh well, I did go back and CR them.  Turned out one of their group had lost a corpse down there and they needed some dragging. <p>Mosushi, Lizard Master of the Fish<br>
